  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The object of this study was to evaluate the accuracy and safety of the Tirobot system.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Tirobot system is a new-type medical robot-assisted surgery system that designed for spine
      and traumatic orthopaedic surgeries. This system has been certified by CE. The accuracy and
      safety of pedicle screw placement using this system will be evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
