  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  traumatic or degenerative thoracolumbar disease required for pedicle screw fixation
             surgery

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  severe osteoporosis

          -  old thoracolumbar fracture

          -  deformity of pedicle

          -  combined with coagulation disorders

          -  combined with other systematic disease
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
